<h2 local-id=3D"17af1d043949" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-4.DevelopmentPractices">4. Development Pr=
actices</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"2ff2112cbed8" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-4.1VersionControl">4.1 Version Control</h=
3>
<p local-id=3D"13d29e5385eb">GitLab CE is used as the self-hosted version c=
ontrol system for this project.</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"37e20237aa39"><strong>Repository Structure:</strong> A GitLa=
b group (<code>karna-grp</code>) was created to organize projects under a n=
amespace. The Flask application repository (<code>task-22-karna</code>) was=
 created inside this group.</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"79d447780fa4"><strong>Repository URL:</strong> <code>http://=
gitlab.karna.pushkar.cloud/karna-grp/task-22-karna.git</code></p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f9a77b29dcd4"><strong>Branching Strategy:</strong> A single =
<code>main</code> branch was used for this PoC. In production, a Git branch=
ing strategy such as GitFlow (main, develop, feature branches) is recommend=
ed.</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0dcc8a6fa9fe"><strong>Code Review:</strong> For this PoC, di=
rect push to <code>main</code> was used. In production, Merge Requests (MRs=
) with peer review should be enforced before merging into main.</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c2334459bc5f"><strong>Commit Practices:</strong> An initial =
commit with message <code>"new"</code> was made. In production, descriptive=
 commit messages following a convention (e.g., Conventional Commits) are re=
commended.</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"cd5d338a3a3b"><strong>Repository Management:</strong> The re=
pository is managed entirely on the self-hosted GitLab CE instance with roo=
t-level admin access.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"23bfc8c548a8" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-4.2ContinuousIntegration">4.2 Continuous =
Integration</h3>
<p local-id=3D"728796f77c6c">In this PoC implementation, CI pipelines were =
not configured. However, GitLab CE supports GitLab CI/CD natively through <=
code>.gitlab-ci.yml</code> files.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c133fe1cd86c"><strong>Recommended future CI setup:</strong><=
/p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8da91ea04cec">Add a <code>.gitlab-ci.yml</code> to the repos=
itory</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b14e9106942e">Define stages: build, test, deploy</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"de4f40ae326c">Use GitLab Runner (installed on EC2 or a separ=
ate runner instance) to execute jobs</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2f499c7b858e">Automate Flask application testing and linting=
 on every push to main</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"75e9e6b37260" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-4.3AutomatedTesting">4.3 Automated Testin=
g</h3>
<p local-id=3D"1914009866da">Automated testing was not implemented in this =
PoC as the focus was on GitLab CE server setup and code push validation.</p=
>
<p local-id=3D"002884e0a9e7"><strong>Recommended future testing setup:</str=
ong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d157ed1347e4">Unit tests using <code>pytest</code> for the F=
lask application</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"aa9cd2684ac0">Integration tests to validate API endpoints</p=
></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6d4b94dd7f9f">Tests integrated into the GitLab CI pipeline v=
ia <code>.gitlab-ci.yml</code></p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"b868f1f07281" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-4.4CodeQualityandAnalysis">4.4 Code Quali=
ty and Analysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"8c408ac9d489">Code quality tooling was not configured in thi=
s PoC.</p>
<p local-id=3D"b8a70483eb88"><strong>Recommended future setup:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"53db3104d4de"><code>flake8</code> or <code>pylint</code> for=
 Python static code analysis</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2bec948fd17d"><code>black</code> for Python code formatting<=
/p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"1babd8afa796">GitLab Code Quality reports integrated into Me=
rge Requests</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"180aaf00db38">Pre-commit hooks to enforce standards locally =
before push</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"1e7629875389" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-5.DeploymentandReleaseManagement">5. Depl=
oyment and Release Management</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"99784b344a34" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-5.1DeploymentStrategy">5.1 Deployment Str=
ategy</h3>
<p local-id=3D"f79987749a82">For this PoC, a direct push to the <code>main<=
/code> branch strategy was used. No formal deployment pipeline was implemen=
ted.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ebf3db67ba20"><strong>Recommended production deployment stra=
tegy:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e7bc1bd8332c">Use GitLab CI/CD with a defined pipeline</p></=
li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7c91c7e5ce80">Adopt a rolling update or blue-green deploymen=
t strategy for Flask app deployments</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4a99bee24843">Use environment-specific branches (develop =E2=
=86=92 staging =E2=86=92 main/production)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"628b275c7244" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-5.2ConfigurationManagement">5.2 Configura=
tion Management</h3>
<p local-id=3D"8dba0c5eb2c9">GitLab CE configuration is managed through the=
 <code>/etc/gitlab/gitlab.rb</code> file on the EC2 instance.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c69fecf9c71e"><strong>Key configuration actions performed:</=
strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"2=
943e511-d832-4163-a583-f307c255793f" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"9c51f0b9acaa">Configuration</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5c87b7ad2f95">Command / Action</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7b4c9122536e">Set custom domain</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fb938709cba1"><code>external_url 'http://gitlab.karna.pushka=
r.cloud'</code> in gitlab.rb</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ca665db6257e">Apply configuration changes</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3a446b2a1f01"><code>sudo gitlab-ctl reconfigure</code></p></=
td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ff999cd1ff21">Upgrade to HTTPS</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ae015e7ea68a">Updated <code>external_url</code> to <code>htt=
ps://</code> and reconfigured</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"00c0e0c4668b">View initial root password</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"118be0b4c752"><code>sudo cat /etc/gitlab/initial_root_passwo=
rd</code></p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"4d53fa38408a">All configuration changes are applied by editi=
ng <code>/etc/gitlab/gitlab.rb</code> and running <code>sudo gitlab-ctl rec=
onfigure</code>, which is GitLab's built-in configuration management mechan=
ism based on Chef.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"f9f5c3742302" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-5.3ContinuousDeliveryandDeployment">5.3 C=
ontinuous Delivery and Deployment</h3>
<p local-id=3D"d5e97035f786">CD was not implemented in this PoC. The code w=
as manually pushed to the GitLab repository using Git CLI commands from the=
 local Windows machine.</p>
<p local-id=3D"85afb89c0926"><strong>Manual deployment process followed:</s=
trong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"876879683dbf">Code prepared locally on Windows machine</p></=
li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6a3cced5e1a7">Git repository initialized and code committed<=
/p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"38bc4ad8a4f8">Remote set to GitLab CE repository URL</p></li=
>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"95c38d4983cd">Code pushed via <code>git push origin main</co=
de></p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4fe0e1b4de78">Code verified visually in the GitLab CE web UI=
</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"37875182aed9"><strong>Recommended future CD setup:</strong><=
/p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6fa5c5d2bfbd">GitLab CI/CD pipeline auto-deploys Flask app t=
o a target server on every merge to main</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6364bb03c150">Approval gates for production deployments</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"0c144de823cd" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-6.MonitoringandIncidentManagement">6. Mon=
itoring and Incident Management</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"aa8cfd611212" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-6.1MonitoringToolsandMetrics">6.1 Monitor=
ing Tools and Metrics</h3>
<p local-id=3D"a274fcf751d6">For this PoC, no external monitoring tools wer=
e configured. GitLab CE provides basic built-in monitoring.</p>
<p local-id=3D"1349bc28a371"><strong>Built-in GitLab CE monitoring:</strong=
></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"30b3d8be8725"><code>sudo gitlab-ctl status</code> =E2=80=94 =
checks the status of all GitLab services (nginx, puma, sidekiq, postgresql,=
 redis, etc.)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b8946fe99143">GitLab Admin Area provides basic system health=
 information via the web UI</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"308ebf0f8fba"><strong>Recommended production monitoring setu=
p:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"42017e1d9016">AWS CloudWatch for EC2 instance metrics (CPU, =
memory, disk)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"074b048aea22">Prometheus + Grafana integrated with GitLab CE=
 for application-level metrics</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5e0cc3d46684">GitLab's built-in Prometheus integration (avai=
lable in gitlab.rb)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"a058b94624a6" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-6.2AlertingandNotification">6.2 Alerting =
and Notification</h3>
<p local-id=3D"5a270f1978f0">No alerting was configured for this PoC.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c9c6e94c5cef"><strong>Recommended production alerting:</stro=
ng></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"938ff3d19a65">AWS CloudWatch Alarms for EC2 CPU/memory thres=
holds</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"107b53a57b0d">GitLab email notifications (via Postfix) for r=
epository events, failed pipelines, and security alerts</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ab6bc33e4d48">PagerDuty or Slack integration for critical in=
cident escalation</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"5be8b61d75a6" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-6.3IncidentManagement">6.3 Incident Manag=
ement</h3>
<p local-id=3D"481ec54eb4a9">No formal incident management process was impl=
emented for this PoC.</p>
<p local-id=3D"e5a272a7ab9b"><strong>Recommended production incident manage=
ment:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"3=
3a742ae-e1cf-47b1-87a8-dd36636c9291" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"ce3b0a4a3c8d">Step</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"70c496ce8d0b">Action</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d5c1c1c25eba">Detection</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cdbdfaf98fad">CloudWatch or GitLab alert triggers</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1002bdff994f">Notification</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"39d4137597b3">Alert sent to on-call DevOps engineer via emai=
l/Slack</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"98436b2db071">Triage</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8747509d67b3">DevOps engineer assesses severity and impact</=
p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"816054a7804e">Resolution</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f23e40e8f30b">Issue resolved; <code>sudo gitlab-ctl restart<=
/code> if services are down</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a4c7ba077a06">Post-mortem</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"840fbee17578">Root cause documented; preventive measures add=
ed</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"6a910235e523" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-7.SecurityandCompliance">7. Security and =
Compliance</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"236e7960c8c4" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-7.1InfrastructureSecurity">7.1 Infrastruc=
ture Security</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"2=
6724021-92a5-4d51-88e1-edec659173cb" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"3c62b63c4e2c">Security Measure</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"76b801a27c3c">Implementation</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5f4a4f56c603">SSH Access Control</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"efdc8559bada">EC2 accessed only via PEM key (<code>t-22-k.pe=
m</code>); password-based SSH disabled</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"652f993c6b1b">Security Group Rules</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"06169b0ebe95">Inbound rules restricted to ports 22 (SSH), 80=
 (HTTP), 443 (HTTPS) only</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"00d886e5c69c">Custom Domain</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c53772d5cc90">GitLab accessible via named domain, not raw EC=
2 IP</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bbf64d2ee42b">HTTPS Upgrade</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4b1fa47d4e7a">GitLab reconfigured from HTTP to HTTPS using u=
pdated <code>external_url</code> in gitlab.rb</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c0f2c9297699">Initial Password</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f2512d786da5">Root password retrieved immediately from <code=
>/etc/gitlab/initial_root_password</code> and changed after first login</p>=
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4b141b1de58c">EC2 Updates</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d68a4348f37a">System packages updated via <code>sudo apt upd=
ate</code> before GitLab installation</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"70bbb4bc48ab" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-7.2IdentityandAccessManagement(IAM)">7.2 =
Identity and Access Management (IAM)</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"2=
b408faa-48ef-442e-ba56-873d06d9ba45" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"cd6b05348a79">IAM Practice</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"bf8f1711a166">Implementation</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8b1cca9a2b9e">Root Account</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"84015eeed377">Used for initial setup; a non-root GitLab user=
 should be created for daily operations in production</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"110e8e43339a">GitLab Groups</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b3725415fb93"><code>karna-grp</code> group created to namesp=
ace projects and control access</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"923ab199b322">Repository Permissions</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b97df798e3b5">Project access controlled via GitLab project v=
isibility settings</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2491bf52ceef">Git Authentication</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9ba52bde9358">Root password used for initial push; Personal =
Access Tokens (PAT) recommended for ongoing automation</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8317745c3a94">SSH Keys</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cf18435e48e0">SSH keys should be added to GitLab user profil=
e for SSH-based Git operations</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"e1b87086d6bd"><strong>Recommended additional security harden=
ing:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e81fd1e150c3">Enable Two-Factor Authentication (2FA) for all=
 GitLab users</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"906d51dbb782">Disable root login for daily use; create admin=
 users with limited scope</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c8d35c70b1db">Rotate Personal Access Tokens periodically</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c15e052d4fa2">Enable GitLab Audit Logs for tracking user and=
 repository activity</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8cbd7562e9f3">Apply HTTPS-only policy; disable plain HTTP ac=
cess after HTTPS upgrade</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
