<h3 local-id=3D"4c54ab5609e3" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-8.2CostOptimizationRecommendations">8.2 C=
ost Optimization Recommendations</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7b6c9820a2dd"><strong>Right-sizing:</strong> Use t3.medium a=
s the minimum; scale up only if GitLab performance degrades</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"96872d2b2c92"><strong>Reserved Instances:</strong> Purchase =
a 1-year Reserved Instance for the EC2 to save ~30=E2=80=9340% vs On-Demand=
 pricing</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"859b11030007"><strong>Storage tiering:</strong> Use gp3 EBS =
volumes (cheaper than gp2) for GitLab data storage</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5c814af74465"><strong>Stop when idle:</strong> During non-bu=
siness hours (for PoC/dev environments), stop the EC2 instance to avoid com=
pute costs; use Elastic IP to retain the public IP</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"c34ff94dced9" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-8.3BusinessValueAnalysis">8.3 Business Va=
lue Analysis</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"e=
