<p local-id=3D"e675dcc9720a">Cost Savings</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"af20b25872b3">Significantly lower cost than SaaS DevOps plat=
forms for growing teams</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e1b1005386a0">Security Control</p></td>
