r Registry, and Wiki at no additional license cost</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ed106c1de5b1">Team Capability</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"520046bea5db">Intern team gains hands-on experience with rea=
l-world DevOps infrastructure setup</p></td>
</tr>
