<h2 local-id=3D"4429047ff730" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-11.ContinuousImprovement">11. Continuous =
Improvement</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"831022e84dea" id=3D"Task22-SettingUpaGitLabCEServerandPushi=
ngaFlaskHelloWorldApplicationcode-11.1FeedbackandRetrospectives">11.1 Feedb=
ack and Retrospectives</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d1b81bf970bc">Post-implementation review to be conducted wit=
h the DevOps team to identify friction points in the setup process</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"663809661807">Feedback collected from developers on usabilit=
y of the self-hosted GitLab instance (access speed, UI, clone/push performa=
nce)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b5a971269239">Retrospective questions: What went well? What =
took longer than expected? What would be done differently?</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ba75a25c5f7e">Key finding from this implementation: The <cod=
e>--allow-unrelated-histories</code> flag was needed during <code>git pull<=
/code> due to remote repository initialization mismatch =E2=80=94 this shou=
ld be documented as a known issue for future interns</p></li>
</ul>
